c: 35
v: 43
t: “Chifukwa cha kudzikweza pa dziko ndi kuchita chiwembu choipa. Ndipo chiwembu choipa sichingamuzinge aliyense koma mwini (yemwe) wachitayo. Kodi akuyembekeza china chosakhala machitidwe (a Allah) amene adawapititsa pa anthu akale. Koma supeza kusintha pa machitidwe a Allah. Ndipo supeza kutembenuka pa machitidwe a Allah